column5: Some of you might remember my report a little less than 8 weeks ago about our Black Lab, Sheba having puppies.  Well they went from this...     To this...in just 7.5 weeks   And now that the 3 we aren't keeping have left the "nest" and are gone to their new homes, we can devote all our time to our newest family member, Princess.  (Averie named her) Wait t'il i'm at the launch callin' her into the boat...Here Princess! lol ah well.    She's an awesome dog, and is learning the ropes real quick from Sheba.  Now I've got 3 fishing partners, and am looking forward to getting out in the boat!  Have a good week @ the office!  Cheers Ryan
awesome ryan! they are so cute!! the pic of u holding the 3 of them... that is that FATTEST puppy i have ever seen! lol

Man did they ever put on the weight in just little time Princess' looking good Ryan I'm sure she'll be a great dog!!!
